ent-WeaponTurretDrakeApolloMk2 = D-20 Apollo MK2 mining laser cannon
    .desc = A Drake Industries rework of the Apollo mining laser. Slower, heavier beams shatter asteroid and supercompacted rock, teleporting mined ore to a point just below the turret.

ent-WeaponTurretDrakeApolloMk2Portable = D-20 Apollo MK2 mining laser cannon
    .desc = { ent-WeaponTurretDrakeApolloMk2.desc }

ent-WeaponTurretDrakeApolloMk2Circuitboard = Apollo MK2 mining laser machine board
    .desc = An upgraded machine printed circuit board for a Drake Industries D-20 Apollo MK2 mining laser cannon. Used with a naval weapon fabricator.

ent-WeaponTurretDrakeApolloMk2Flatpack = Apollo MK2 mining laser flatpack
    .desc = A flatpack used for constructing a Drake Industries Apollo MK2 mining laser cannon.
